criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 18 and 45 years;

          -  Surgery required by pelvic pain or infertility related to endometriosis;

          -  Clinical and imaging data proving unilateral ovarian endometrioma which diameter
             exceeds 30 mm.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous surgery on ovaries or IVF procedures;

          -  Bilateral endometriomas;

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Woman not French speaker.
